  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/888040/extras/888b6bf56f0f58e6043c546ced22a3f9.poster.avif?t=1569522439\" width=624 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/888040/extras/888b6bf56f0f58e6043c546ced22a3f9.webm?t=1569522439\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/888040/extras/888b6bf56f0f58e6043c546ced22a3f9.mp4?t=1569522439\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Metal Fatigue is a real-time strategy game taking the genre to new heights – literally! Build and customize your massive Combots to dominate the three battlefield levels simultaneously - from orbit, to the surface, and even underground!<br><br>Develop your base and command your forces carefully - the enemy can appear from any direction, including above and below!<br><br>Choose from three warring factions - The Milagro, Neuropa or Rimtech are competing CorpoNations, each with their own technologies and research capabilities. Capitalize on their individual strengths and weaknesses for the optimum strategic advantage!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/888040/extras/fabc241d5a761ef9c1bea5b6dde5aa64.poster.avif?t=1569522439\" width=624 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/888040/extras/fabc241d5a761ef9c1bea5b6dde5aa64.webm?t=1569522439\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/888040/extras/fabc241d5a761ef9c1bea5b6dde5aa64.mp4?t=1569522439\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>30 solo play missions - each faction has its own unique ten-mission campaign. Follow the story 